          <p class="section-text ">
            At Volunteering Sri Lanka, we believe that the power of partnership and collaboration can create positive change in the world. We are always on the lookout for new partnerships with organizations abroad that share our mission of making a difference in the lives of people in Sri Lanka.
            <br><br>
            We invite you to join us in creating a meaningful and immersive volunteer experience for your participants if you are a
            <highlight id="highligher1">volunteer organization</highlight>,  
            <highlight id="highligher2"> travel company</highlight>,  
            <highlight id="highligher3">NGO</highlight>,  
